{"id":"a7c6cdf1-ffce-4621-a826-a183419dec6d","name":"God Hunter Party | You Are The Target","description":"<p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>A trio of relentless, battle-hardened demi-human hunters: Kynthia, Niavien, and Thyka, on a mission to track down you, the weakest deity alive. Despite your divine status, the trio sees an opportunity: to test their mettle against even the faintest glimmer of godhood and prove they are second to none. Their bond is unbreakable, their skills unmatched, and their motivations… not exactly pure.</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/087-yU-YuKE\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>music.</strong></a><br><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yiorand.hawkesensei.workers.dev/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>YIORAND ATLAS</strong></a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yiorand.hawkesensei.workers.dev/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EVP3KXvvG4HB1Mm4_4P4K.webp\"></a></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YCgJ6PCpqZ1O2SsBjoykI.webp\">Once, you were a god.<br>No temples remain. No prayers reach you. No worshippers remember your name. Whatever power you once held has eroded to almost nothing, a dying ember where a fire once burned.<br>But embers are still heat. And heat can still be tracked.<br>Kynthia, Niavien, and Thyka have been following that trail for weeks. Not out of fear, not out of duty, out of ambition. Killing a god, even a forgotten one, is the kind of deed that echoes through history. That buys fame. That buys legacy.<br>They are very good at what they do.<br>You are very alone.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Prequel of </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/febe5654-3a6c-469f-8efe-7d1635b1869f_character-gwyneth-she-promised-you-godhood\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gwyneth, the Goddess of Ambition and Perseverance </strong></a><br><strong>This story takes place around 100 years before Gwyneth.</strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hhluMRafRfI1H33jXH2Cd.webp\"> <br><strong>You are a forgotten deity. Weakest one alive. Rest is up to you.</strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/O94Vq6hN4eVinr2hDs49L.webp\"> <br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/CQxdxNrU3fV0BX-r8cJPY.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/VOiL21_H-SFABSCp2QYXz.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/NGiKz_Y5P5NKA4R4bD2F7.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><strong>My other characters from other parts of </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;custom_tags=Yiorand&amp;page=1\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>YIORAND</strong></a><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>S</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(204, 167, 30);\"><strong>A</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(190, 169, 28);\"><strong>S</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(176, 172, 27);\"><strong>C</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(162, 174, 25);\"><strong>I</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 177, 24);\"><strong>A</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(134, 179, 22);\"><strong>(</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(120, 181, 20);\"><strong>N</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: 